# Example blocklist — one bare domain per line. '#' and blank lines are ignored.
# Copy this to "blocklist" (the script does it for you on first run), then edit
# with `focus add <url>` / `focus rm <url>`. Your real blocklist stays local and
# is gitignored, so it is never published.
youtube.com
twitter.com
reddit.com
news.ycombinator.com
facebook.com
instagram.com
